title: Eurovision.Song.Contest.2016.SF2.EBU-FEED.reenc.720p.AC3-icecube
description:
This is the 720p re-encode of the original 1920*1080i EBU feed transport stream posted. Size really doesn't matter! ;)

Original feed ts posted by Anonymous as: Eurovision Song Contest 2016: Stockholm (2nd SF) [FEED 1080i]

WORDS OF CAUTION WHEN PLAYING BACK!

Media player tests/comparison. Players used:
VLC 2.2.1
MS Media player Ver. 12.07601.19148
MPC+HC Media Player Classic with CCCP:MPC 64-bit 1.7.8.162/CCCP Raise Your Flag 2015-10-18

Playing back my 720p re-encode:
MPC: No colour issues. No discernible image/sound sync issues at the end.
VLC: Colour issues, but lesser. No jump issues. No artifacts. No sync issues.
MS Media Player: Opens in small window but will go full screen. No colour, jump or sync issues. behaves well.

Recommended media player is still the CCCP package with the Media Player Classic found at http://www.cccp-project.net/
